      <title></title>
      <link>/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am a PhD student at Inria working in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://team.inria.fr/magnet/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Magnet&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://team.inria.fr/multispeech/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Multispeech&lt;/a&gt; team. I am supervised by &lt;a href=&#34;http://researchers.lille.inria.fr/abellet/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Dr. Aurélien Bellet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://members.loria.fr/EVincent/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Dr. Emmanuel Vincent&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://researchers.lille.inria.fr/tommasi/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Dr. Marc Tommasi&lt;/a&gt;. My work mainly focuses towards privacy-preserving speech processing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Check out the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.voiceprivacychallenge.org/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;1st Voice Privacy Challenge&lt;/a&gt; to know more about the privacy benchmarks we obtained using our baseline and participate to evaluate your own anonymization methods.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
